# User-Provided Gemini API Key Implementation Plan

Users should be able to provide their own Gemini API key in real-time. This key will be used for genre detection, replacing or augmenting the default key.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> - The API key will be stored locally on the device using Jetpack DataStore.
> - If no user key is provided, the app will fallback to the default key provided in `BuildConfig.GEMINI_API_KEY`.
> - The UI will include a way to see the current key (masked) and update it.

